Name: SSN
display:km: លេខសំគាល់សន្តិសុខសង្គម
Format description: Identifier should be 1 letter, followed by a dash and 7 numerical characters. Eg, A-0010902

Name: National ID
display:km: អត្ថ​សញ្ញាណ​ប​ណ្ណ​ជាតិ
Format description: National ID should be 9 digits. E.g, 923456678. If the ID is renewed, it will have (xx) appended at the end, where xx represent the iteration of card renewed e.g (01) for first renewal, (02) for second renewal, and so on.

Name: Passport No
display:km: លេខលិខិតឆ្លងដែន

Name: COVID vaccination ID
display:km: លេខសម្គាល់ការចាក់វ៉ាក់សាំង COVID
Format description: COVID Identifier should be 10 numbers, separated by dashes. Eg, 321-123-1234

Name: IDPoor
display:km: លេខសម្គាល់ប័ណ្ណក្រីក្រ (ប័ណ្ឌមូលនិធិសមធម៌)
Format description: IDPoor identifier should be formatted as 'Pre-ID' (Eg, 12345678-1234), 'Post ID CTP' (12345678-5123), 'Post ID' (Eg, 12345678-9ddd), Patient ID' (Eg, 123-123-123-1) or 'Informal Worker ID' (Eg, 1234567-1234567-9)

Name: NSSF
display:km: បេឡាជាតិសន្តិសុខសង្គម
Format description: NSSF Identifier should be 15 numbers, separated by dashes. Eg, 2343453-1234567-9

Name: PMRS ID
display:km: លេខសម្គាល់ប្រព័ន្ធកត់ត្រា និងគ្រប់គ្រងអ្នកជំងឺអេឡិចត្រូនិក
Format description: PMRS Identifier should be 10 numbers, separated by dashes. Eg, 321-123-123-4
